OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773370999
OL,3,CLeaders unite against replacing
OL,4,Chistorical figures on banknotes with
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FReplacing figures including Sir
OL,8,FWinston Churchill with images of
OL,9,Fwildlife on the next series of Bank of
OL,10,FEngland banknotes is "erasing our
OL,11,Fhistory", Kemi Badenoch has said.
OL,13,FThe Conservative leader, who described
OL,14,Fherself as a "huge fan" of Churchill,
OL,15,Fdescribed the government's plan to
OL,16,Foverhaul the UK's banknotes -
OL,17,Fannounced on Wednesday - as "a silly
OL,18,Fthing to do".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773370999
OL,3,CLeaders unite against replacing
OL,4,Chistorical figures on banknotes with
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FThe central bank's move marks a shift
OL,8,Fafter more than 50 years of showcasing
OL,9,Fpeople from Britain's history on the
OL,10,Fnotes, including Churchill, Alan
OL,11,FTuring and Jane Austen.
OL,13,FThe Bank said the change to wildlife
OL,14,Fimagery creates an opportunity to
OL,15,Fcelebrate another important aspect of
OL,16,Fthe nation.
OL,18,FIt is also said to make it more
OL,19,Fdifficult for the notes to be
OL,20,Fcounterfeited while making security
OL,21,Ffeatures more distinguishable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773370999
OL,3,CLeaders unite against replacing
OL,4,Chistorical figures on banknotes with
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FSpeaking on a visit to North London,
OL,8,FBadenoch suggested former Tory prime
OL,9,Fminister Margaret Thatcher should
OL,10,Ffeature.
OL,12,F"I think that removing Churchill from
OL,13,Fbanknotes is erasing our history. I'm
OL,14,Fa huge fan of Winston Churchill. I
OL,15,Fthink that he is very much believed to
OL,16,Fbe this country's greatest wartime
OL,17,Fprime minister.
OL,19,F"This is not a problem at all. It's
OL,20,Fnot something that needs to be solved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773370999
OL,3,CLeaders unite against replacing
OL,4,Chistorical figures on banknotes with
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,F"If anything, I think that they should
OL,8,Fbe putting more historical figures on
OL,9,Fbanknotes. I would quite like to see
OL,10,FMargaret Thatcher on a banknote. I
OL,11,Fthink she was Britain's greatest
OL,12,Fpeacetime prime minister.
OL,14,F"Changing the pictures to put wild
OL,15,Fanimals on them is a silly thing to
OL,16,Fdo. I absolutely do not support it."
OL,18,FConcerns had previously been raised
OL,19,Fabout the lack of women being featured
OL,20,Fon the notes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773370999
OL,3,CLeaders unite against replacing
OL,4,Chistorical figures on banknotes with
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FFlorence Nightingale was the first,
OL,8,Fappearing on the #10 note in 1975, and
OL,9,Fmore recently Jane Austen was added
OL,10,Fafter a campaign to feature a woman
OL,11,Ffollowing Elizabeth Fry being replaced
OL,12,Fby Churchill.
OL,14,FBadenoch joins calls from the leaders
OL,15,Fof both Reform and the Lib Dems.
OL,17,FWriting on X, Lib Dem Leader Ed Davey
OL,18,Fsaid: "Winston Churchill helped defeat
OL,19,Ffascism in Europe. He deserves better
OL,20,Fthan being replaced by a badger."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773370999
OL,3,CLeaders unite against replacing
OL,4,Chistorical figures on banknotes with
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FHe went on to add: "I can't think of a
OL,8,Fworse time to do this, with a war
OL,9,Fwaging in Europe, we should be
OL,10,Fcelebrating Britain's defiance of the
OL,11,FNazis.
OL,13,F"I love nature as much as anyone else,
OL,14,Fbut for goodness sake, let's celebrate
OL,15,Four wonderful British wildlife, sure,
OL,16,Fbut Winston Churchill helped save our
OL,17,Fcountry and the whole of Europe from
OL,18,Ffascism."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773370999
OL,3,CLeaders unite against replacing
OL,4,Chistorical figures on banknotes with
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FDavey's intervention signals a rare
OL,8,Fmoment of agreement with Reform UK's
OL,9,Fleader Nigel Farage, who called the
OL,10,Fproposals "PC mad and loony".
OL,12,FThe Bank of England exists
OL,13,Findependently of the government, and
OL,14,Fon Thursday, the prime minister's
OL,15,Fofficial spokesman said: "Banknote
OL,16,Fdesign is an operational matter for
OL,17,Fthe independent Bank of England."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
