PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773370999
OL,3,CLeaders unite against replacing
OL,4,Chistorical figures on banknotes with
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FThe Bank's move follows a consultation
OL,8,Fin which the UK wildlife theme
OL,9,Freceived the highest proportion of
OL,10,Fnominations, at 60%.
OL,12,FArchitecture and landmarks was a close
OL,13,Fsecond at 56%, followed by notable
OL,14,Fhistorical figures (38%), arts,
OL,15,Fculture and sport (30%), innovation
OL,16,F(23%) and noteworthy milestones (19%).
OL,18,FMore than 44,000 responses were
OL,19,Freceived, including from online
OL,20,Fsurveys, emails and designs submitted
OL,21,Fby schools and the public.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773370999
OL,3,CLeaders unite against replacing
OL,4,Chistorical figures on banknotes with
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FA second consultation will be run this
OL,8,Fsummer to gather views on the specific
OL,9,Fwildlife they would like to feature,
OL,10,Fwhich can include plants, landscapes,
OL,11,Fand animals.
OL,13,FIt will be several years before the
OL,14,Fbanknotes are issued, and they will
OL,15,Fcontinue to show a portrait of the
OL,16,Fmonarch.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
