PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773370999
OL,3,CLeaders unite against replacing
OL,4,Chistorical figures on banknotes with
OL,5,Canimals
OL,7,FVictoria Cleland, chief cashier at the
OL,8,FBank of England, said: "The key driver
OL,9,Ffor introducing a new banknote series
OL,10,Fis always to increase counterfeit
OL,11,Fresilience, but it also provides an
OL,12,Fopportunity to celebrate different
OL,13,Faspects of the UK.
OL,15,F"Nature is a great choice from a
OL,16,Fbanknote authentication perspective
OL,17,Fand means we can showcase the UK's
OL,18,Frich and varied wildlife on the next
OL,19,Fseries of banknotes.
OL,26,@pD@XOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
